The focus is on communication channels, which suggests the networking and internet architecture sub-category (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the sparsity of generating matrices, which is a topic in compressed sensing (cs.DS). The paper proposes a suboptimal decoder, which is a topic in signal processing (cs.SI).
